{"pred": "The third annual XR Technology Forum concluded with a discussion of the industry's development and baseline assumptions. \n\nKnowing that there are many different ways to approach the same problem, the forum participants shared their experiences of live business development over the past few years. For example, they discussed the following:\n\n- VR 1:1 headset vs. AR glasses\n- AML baseline for AR/VR applications\n- HR technology and future judgments\n- Business opportunities and investment potential\n- Technical limitations and ways to overcome them\n\nIn summary, the forum aimed to provide a richer understanding of the complex challenges facing XR technology, through the collective insights of its diverse participants.", "answers": ["会议确定了AR及VR落地于游戏场景，应用于工业化感受远程现场，包括品牌广告，娱乐，工业教育，公号提供设备刚需，结合声色声线，交互机制明确定位等场景，交互环节在三次空间中进行，在没有网格或其他形式的系统中可以把对应环境转变为数据以网格形式进行交互，过程中面临功能配置多样化，功耗，创新落地之后的负责量，理解问题的深度，解决问题的难度等挑战，在光学意识算法中不断深耕，提高基础要求，明确定位，实现核心突破，预期在未来VR及AR领域能实现初级普及，VR眼镜实现征集游戏第一版本，交互方式突破新的监控能力，未来VR会更换方式，结合更多商店，实现面部识别，动画等功能，探索更多未知领域。"], "all_classes": null, "length": 11982}
